sources.title: The Assassination of Western Civilization | Full Movie 2024 | Mystery Thriller
sources.description:
*The Assassination of Western Civilization* - A tabloid writer has evidence of the assassination of a US Senator. A visit from a scrupulous FBI agent suggests he may know more than he's admitting about the assassination and the key may reside in the recesses of the writer's dark past.
2022.  Stars: Wendy Hartman, Sheri Lee, Jocelyn Padilla
